<%- include ("partials/header") -%>
	<div class="background backgroundWhite"></div>
	<div class="backgroundOverlay"></div>
	<div class="content whiteContent">
		<div class="header">
			<div class="logoWrap">
				<img src="/logos/Vinfo_white.svg" width="50">
			</div>
			<div class="powered">
				Powered by <a href="#">vinfo.rs</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="mainTitle">Sava Minić</div>
		<div class="videoWrap" data-fullscreen="0">
			<div style="position:relative">
				<video>
					<source src="/videos/proizvodnja-belo.mp4" type="video/mp4">
				</video>
				<div class="overlay" onclick="playVideo(this.parentElement.parentElement)"></div>
				<img src="/icons/Play-Button.png" class="playButton" onclick="playVideo(this.parentElement.parentElement)">
				<div class="playerClose" onclick="playVideo(this.parentElement.parentElement)">X</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="bottleWrap">
			<div class="imageWrap">
				<img src="/images/Sava-Minic-Belo.png">
			</div>
			<div class="bottleInfo">
				<div class="title">Sava Minić</div>
				<div class="subTitle">Tamjanika - <span class="thin">Belo vino</span></div>
				<div class="paragraph">
					Sava Minić Tamjanika 2018 je napravljen tradicionalnim načinom od sorte grožđa Tamjanika. Baš takvog ga pravi, neguje i čuva na svom porodničnom imanju, poznati vinar Sava Minić sa svojim naslednicima. Vino se odlikuje zlatno zutom bojom i harmoničnim ukusom. Da bi pokazalo lepotu ukusa, arome-bukea treba ga konzumirati od 8-10°C.
				</div>
				<div class="wineContentsWrap">
					<div class="subTitle">Sastav:</div>
					<div class="wineContentWrap">
						<div class="name">
							Tamjanika (100%) - 
						</div>
						<div class="percentage">
							<div class="powerBar" data-power="100"></div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="subTitle">
						Berba:
					</div>
					<div>2018</div>
				</div>
				<div class="temperatureWrap">
					<div class="subTitle">Serviranje:</div>
					<div class="temperatureIconWrap">
						<img src="/icons/Vinfo_white_Temp.svg" width="100">
						<div class="temperature">
							9&#176;C
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="mapWrap">
					<div class="subTitle">Poreklo:</div>
					<div id="map"></div>
					<script>
						var map;
						var myLatLng;
						var marker;

						function initMap() {
							myLatLng = {lat: 43.477808, lng: 21.086015};
							map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById('map'), {
								center: myLatLng,
								zoom: 12
							});
							marker = new google.maps.Marker({
								position: myLatLng,
								map: map,
								title: 'Poreklo',
								icon: '/icons/white_map_pin.png'
							});
						}
					</script>
					<script src="https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=AIzaSyAsUyoMs0Ba_6bPbtD5A5_1yOJXjjMYsMQ&amp;callback=initMap" async="" defer=""></script>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<script src="/js/videoControls.js"></script>
<%- include ("partials/footer") -%>